    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《Fateful Night》是一款以剧情为核心的心理惊悚游戏，讲述了四位大学生寻找刺激的故事。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>剧情：</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你将以其中一名学生——吉姆的视角展开冒险。他与女友和朋友们一同前往森林深处的一座废弃宅邸——这是他们的朋友瑞恩推荐的地方。警方对此地毫无记录，于是他们决定抢先一步前去探索。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3251590/extras/96e24e68ed8e6c9d4c665ad49035bef6.poster.avif?t=1746544000\" width=616 height=264 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3251590/extras/96e24e68ed8e6c9d4c665ad49035bef6.webm?t=1746544000\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3251590/extras/96e24e68ed8e6c9d4c665ad49035bef6.mp4?t=1746544000\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>玩法：</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >本作是一款叙事驱动的步行模拟游戏，注重氛围、紧张感与人物互动。 <br>大部分玩法围绕对话展开，玩家将通过与其他角色的互动作出关键选择。每个角色都会对你的言语和行为做出回应，而你的决定可能会改变故事的走向和朋友们的命运。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3251590/extras/86f5c62569c4a99367ebce8a7d84b90e.poster.avif?t=1746544000\" width=616 height=264 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3251590/extras/86f5c62569c4a99367ebce8a7d84b90e.webm?t=1746544000\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3251590/extras/86f5c62569c4a99367ebce8a7d84b90e.mp4?t=1746544000\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>你们能否全部平安回家？还是有人永远无法参加下一次考试？</strong><br>一切将在这个<i>命运之夜</i>揭晓。</p>",
